{"tid":1247653,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"高圓圓四度飲恨 劉亦菲女神奪冠","createTime":"2019-06-21T07:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T12:26:18.000Z","uid":85180,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"62163855e29b9f71aec20f39a970800be5b13896","tid":1247653,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:37:36.000Z","msg":"高圓圓四度飲恨 劉亦菲女神奪冠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/880f0e4aly1g42720a12aj20p212y4qp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F880f0e4aly1g42720a12aj20p212y4qp.jpg&h=e1c93b1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地女星劉亦菲向來有「仙氣女神」之稱，最近入圍內地網站舉辦的「第四屆直男女神選舉」，並成功在64位來自中、日、韓的女星之中脫穎而出，與剛榮升人母的女星高圓圓躋身決賽，最後她以51.3%的得票率，登上冠軍寶座！不少網友對結果表示滿意，直呼「劉亦菲奪冠是意料之中」、「劉亦菲根本是神仙顏值」。不過，有網友對以48.7%得票僅敗、第四度奪亞的高圓圓大感可惜，力壓她的前三屆冠軍女神分別是台灣女星賈靜雯、一代性感女神邱淑貞以及新疆美女佟麗婭。"},{"pid":"6845cfe1ee8c8e6d1a8507cc9b8a21780b0b8156","tid":1247653,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:48:05.000Z","msg":"覺得柳岩,王李丹妮果種大波女人正D<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1799a1451a22ee5fbb956f12e82d6c7bed108afd","tid":1247653,"uid":213285,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:48:49.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"7535c7d284636bf749c5b30f1dd494becfc9e0af","tid":1247653,"uid":118973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"個格肋底想點"},{"pid":"af5cedeac11e7327d5c7b7001df5c714e09e6046","tid":1247653,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1799a1451a22ee5fbb956f12e82d6c7bed108afd","tid":1247653,"uid":213285,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:48:49.000Z","msg":"Who?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"on9 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},